data.text:
I.B.I [DISBAND]

I.B.I was a project girl group that debuted in 2016 with the song, "Molae Molae." The group was made up of Haein, Sohee, Suhyun, Chaekyung, and Hyeri. They are managed by LOEN Entertainment. The group is made up of contestants from the Top 22 of Produce 101​ who didn't make it in the final line up of I.O.I Like I.OI, they are expected to promote and disband after a year and will return to their own companies and will return to training or get ready to debut in a group under their respective companies. They disbanded in January of 2017 and all members returned to their respective companies/groups.
